281 economical and efficient manner and that is adequate to permit
282 the provision of care and services necessary to attain or
283 maintain the highest practicable, physical, mental, and
284 psychosocial well-being of each resident eligible for Alabama
285 Medicaid nursing home benefits in conformity with applicable
286 state and federal laws, rules, and regulations and quality and
